org.gvsig.exportto

Interface ExporttoManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultExporttoManager

    public interface ExporttoManager
    This class is responsible of the management of the library's business logic. It is the library's main entry point, and provides all the services to manage ExporttoServices.
